short_description.value:
We provide an intuitive, configurable SaaS solution called creatiogreen, 
supporting a variety of organisations offering regulated or non-regulated 
training, courses, products or qualifications. These include Awarding 
Organisations, Membership & Professional Bodies, Charities, Public Sector 
Bodies, End-Point Assessment Organisations and Private Companies - helping 
them to transform their processes.
